channel.title: Don't commit if it wont even compile!
channel.description: This thing is never going to work if we dont use our brains, just now I updated to the latest CVS files, and somone broke somthing to do with the server class and the dialogue class by not calling them correctly in client.java, I did manage however to fix the insane amount of errors I got and commit it, just be careful next time and make sure it compiles before you commit ;) :D
